snippet: A coordinated car bomb and suicide bomb attack on a Shiite mosque in Baghdad killed at least 33 people and wounded 55, the police and medical officials said.
abstract: Coordinated car bomb and suicide bomb attack on a Shiite mosque in Baghdad kills at least 33 people and wounds 55.
